## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/imutkeyvalueinfo">ImutKeyValueInfo</a> -Traits class used by <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/immutablemap">ImmutableMap</a>.

While both the first and second elements in a pair are used to generate profile information, only the first element (the key) is used by isEqual and isLess.

Definition at line 28 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/immutablemap-h">ImmutableMap.h</a>.
